1. Create User benchmarker(pass:benchmark) and make him sudo
adduser benchmarker
sudo usermode -aG sudo benchmarker

2. Install Scala and sbt

3. Install Based on the role of the server the needed packages
3.1 postgres 9.6
3.2 Apache Kafka and Zookeeper (and run as service
3.3 DSPS servers
3.3.1 Apache Spark
3.3.2 Apache Flink
3.3.3 Hazelcast jet
